-- Chrysler recalls thousands of Dodge Ram pickups
-- 
-- Wed Dec 10, 2008 1:22pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/12/10/us-chrysler-recalls-idUSTRE4B95NT20081210

 

 (Reuters) - Chrysler said on Wednesday it was recalling 108,429 Dodge Ram diesel pickup trucks. 

 Highlights: * Says engine compartment flaw in Ram pickup trucks could cause fires * Says expects recall to begin this month * Says has received 14 complaints of Dodge engine fires that may be related to the recall